body:
Hello,
   I am trying a simple SV class code with IVL. Simple class works. Inheritance doesn't compile. I get an error as __../ref/inherit_base.sv:51: assert: elab_scope.cc:503: failed assertion scope__

I am using __-g2012__ already. Am I missing a flag or something please?

Thanks
Srini 

Consider the following code:

```javascript
class s2p_pkt;
 bit [15:0] hdr= 16'd10;
 bit [15:0] pkt_pld=16'd30;

  virtual function bit [31:0] bit_pack();
      bit_pack = {hdr,pkt_pld};
  endfunction : bit_pack

  function void display ();
    $display ("CVC:VSV: Lab3: Learning Inheritence");
    $display ("CVC:VSV: Lab3: Extended class %m has base properties hdr %0b pkt_pld %0b AND Extra err_pkt ", hdr, pkt_pld );
  endfunction : display

endclass : s2p_pkt

class s2p_err_pkt extends s2p_pkt;
endless

```

